creators across the web </em>😊</h3></div><h3 id=\"creating-an-equitable-data-economy-to-value-ecosystem-services-with-david-dao-of-gainforest-the-ownership-economy-podcast\">Creating an Equitable Data Economy to Value Ecosystem Services, with David Dao of GainForest | The Ownership Economy Podcast</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/jahedmomand/\">Jahed Momand</a> sits down with <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/dwddao/\">David Dao</a>, founder of GainForest and PhD candidate at ETH Zurich, to talk about valuing natural assets with the participation of land stewards. They discuss ecosystem services, their economic contribution, ownership regimes, and an equitable future if ecosystem services are included in global GDP while also touching on data governance and ownership.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><iframe style=\"border-radius: 12px\" width=\"100%\" height=\"152\" title=\"Spotify Embed: The Ownership Economy\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen allow=\"autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://open.spotify.com/embed/show/4iq2QLf1YDiF1OZhX8giIk?utm_source=oembed\"></iframe></figure><h3 id=\"refi-summit-with-rex-st-john-the-block-explorer-podcast\">ReFi Summit with Rex St. John | The Block Explorer Podcast</h3><p>Rex St. John shares his perspective about the current status of Regenerative Finance, the upcoming ReFi Summit in Seattle this May, and the intersection of cultural changes and technology.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">what is the state of the <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ReFi?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#ReFi</a> nation? we asked <a href=\"https://twitter.com/rexstjohn?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@rexstjohn</a> who is a deep thinker when it comes to ecosystems.<br><br>you’re going to want to hear his answers. listen 🎧 to episode #74<br>now - it’s for <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/regens?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#regens</a> and <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/degens?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#degens</a> alike! <a href=\"https://t.co/xn8RROKcJE\">https://t.co/xn8RROKcJE</a></p>&mdash; Block Explorer Impact Podcast (@Block_Explore) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Block_Explore/status/1644115744760774656?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">April 6, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><hr><div class=\"kg-card kg-header-card kg-width-full kg-size-small kg-style-image\" style=\"background-image: url(https://blog.refidao.com/content/images/2023/01/ReFi-Cover-1.png)\" data-kg-background-image=\"https://blog.refidao.com/content/images/2023/01/ReFi-Cover-1.png\"><h2 class=\"kg-header-card-header\" id=\"refi-events-%F0%9F%AA%A9\">ReFi Events 🪩</h2><h3 class=\"kg-header-card-subheader\" id=\"emget-your-refi-on-with-friends-in-person-and-onlineem\"><em>Get your ReFi on with friends in-person and online...</em></h3><a href=\"https://refispring.com/\" class=\"kg-header-card-button\">View more</a></div><h2 id=\"explore-refi-events-at-refidaocom-%F0%9F%91%87%F0%9F%8F%BD\">Explore ReFi Events at <a href=\"https://www.refidao.com/ecosystem/events\">ReFiDAO.com</a> 👇🏽</h2><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/03/Screenshot-2023-03-20-at-11.48.15-am.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"678\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2023/03/Screenshot-2023-03-20-at-11.48.15-am.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2023/03/Screenshot-2023-03-20-at-11.48.15-am.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1600/2023/03/Screenshot-2023-03-20-at-11.48.15-am.png 1600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/03/Screenshot-2023-03-20-at-11.48.15-am.png 2196w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption><a href=\"https://www.refidao.com/ecosystem/events\"><