com/groups/12778967/\">ReFi Munich community</a>. The event unites stakeholders across ESG, Regenerative Finance, and Web 3.0 to encourage collaboration for sustainability.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><a href=\"https://www.eventbrite.de/e/refi-summit-digitizing-for-a-sustainable-future-tickets-607549455777\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/04/image-15.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"940\" height=\"470\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2023/04/image-15.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/04/image-15.png 940w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></a></figure><h3 id=\"eth-barcelona-%E2%98%80%EF%B8%8F\"><br><a href=\"https://twitter.com/eth_barcelona\">ETH Barcelona ☀️ </a></h3><p><strong>(July 5th-7th, Barcelona, Spain)</strong></p><p>The biggest ETH event in Spain. With a focus on education, innovation, art, and creating positive social impact. Empowering communities with blockchain education and tools for societal impact.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Calling all creators and artists! 📡👨‍🎤👨‍🎨<br><br>Apply now to share your creations with us at ETHBarcelona 2023 👇<a href=\"https://t.co/6TkAXb3chi\">https://t.co/6TkAXb3chi</a></p>&mdash; ETHBarcelona ( :D , :D ) (@eth_barcelona) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/eth_barcelona/status/1642842378674511878?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">April 3, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><h2 id=\"add-your-refi-event-%F0%9F%91%87%F0%9F%8F%BD\">Add your ReFi event! 👇🏽</h2><p><em>Got a ReFi, crypto, or climate event coming up and what to have it featured in the website &amp; newsletter? Add yours to the database!</em></p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://www.refidao.com/submit-refi-event\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Add your ReFi event</a></div><div class=\"kg-card kg-hea